How-To SYNC your On-Premise AD with AZURE AD (Hands-On) In this Tutorial Blog, We will integrate a Single Forest On-Premise Active Directory (AD) with our Azure Active Directory(AAD) using
Azure AD Connect &gt; &ldquo;Azure AD cloud sync&rdquo;
What is Azure AD Connect cloud sync? Azure AD Connect Cloud Sync is a cloud service alternative to Azure AD Connect software. The organization deploys one or more lightweight agents in their on-premises environment to bridge AD and Azure AD.
